Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.70,0:01:49.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆一行人在旅途中的某个城镇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.45,0:01:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被卷入了一个女孩的梦境中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.17,0:01:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女孩的名字叫史泰拉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.45,0:01:59.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她的身体似乎也受到了卡赞的诅咒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.18,0:02:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由于巴隆他们的踊跃相助
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.99,0:02:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她明白了生存的真正意义
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.24,0:02:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,随后一行人来到了终年积雪的斯顿雪域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.96,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(371,252)}激战
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.19,0:02:18.96,biaoti,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(349,378)}魔之山脊 -前篇-
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.74,0:02:26.35,biaozhu,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯顿雪域
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.11,0:02:38.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.55,0:02:43.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在就冻成这样的话是没办法翻过这座山的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想去泡温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.30,0:02:48.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好耶 温泉 去吧去吧 马上去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.10,0:02:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉的话 也可以治疗鬼手吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.30,0:02:55.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那还用说 泡温泉 消百病嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.81,0:02:56.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.98,0:02:58.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就赶快行动吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.37,0:03:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去给我找温泉
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.22,0:03:04.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是说机器人是倾注了爱心的结晶吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.71,0:03:06.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,动作快点哟
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.67,0:03:08.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种地方还有人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.48,0:03:12.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们怎么了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.75,0:03:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们被班图族袭击了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.66,0:03:19.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,东西全都被洗劫一空了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是我要泼冷水 你们还是下山的好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.42,0:03:28.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族 是什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.68,0:03:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是膜拜斯顿雪域远古山神的部族
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.71,0:03:39.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真快呀 找到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.72,0:03:42.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.11,0:03:44.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.42,0:03:46.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它好像找到了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:47.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈 会不会是温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.22,0:03:52.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底有什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.84,0:03:54.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人倒在那里
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.53,0:03:58.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还好吗 振作点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.91,0:04:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.09,0:04:08.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子 我们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.01,0:04:17.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村子里 村子里来了一群怪人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.73,0:04:29.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰 快起来
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.40,0:04:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.44,0:04:35.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,起来 快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.16,0:04:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快点 没时间跟你解释了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.45,0:04:41.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要干什么 你们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.96,0:04:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想要求救 却掉到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.46,0:05:01.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请救救村子里的人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.63,0:05:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求求你们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.27,0:05:08.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:09.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以别哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.68,0:05:13.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是班图族的对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.69,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是那个袭击旅人的班图族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.65,0:05:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族才不会做那种没品的事
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族可是非常有自豪感的部族
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.54,0:05:35.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的村子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:39.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都被杀害了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.30,0:05:41.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是过分
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:46.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不一定是你想的那样 是被雪崩冲垮的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.22,0:05:51.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才不是 才不是什么雪崩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.73,0:05:53.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡本西斯 你注意到了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.93,0:05:57.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然 右边有两个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.86,0:05:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,左边有三个人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.60,0:06:01.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对 是四个
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:20.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,袭击他们的 是你们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.85,0:06:24.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 是村民
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.09,0:06:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 搞错了 这些人是
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.39,0:06:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.63,0:06:30.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.23,0:06:32.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你没事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.45,0:06:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.92,0:06:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.50,0:06:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.16,0:06:43.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰 你没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.05,0:06:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 我好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.69,0:06:48.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丢下你一个人 对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.33,0:06:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些人救了我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.94,0:06:54.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是班图族的族长 奥尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.72,0:06:58.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,承蒙你们关照小妹 在此谢过
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是偶然路过顺便而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.01,0:07:03.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么 这个村子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.34,0:07:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是 被雪崩冲垮的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.13,0:07:10.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斯顿雪域最近经常这样呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.20,0:07:11.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雪崩
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.91,0:07:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看吧 果然是雪崩嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.26,0:07:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那天晚上 村里的不速之客是什么人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.83,0:07:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要担心 那只是温泉调查团而已
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.29,0:07:28.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,村里的其他人现在正陪他们在视察周围的情况
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:30.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没有什么可担心的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们也赶快下山去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:38.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这座山对外来者说很危险
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.94,0:07:41.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.45,0:07:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.56,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,得快点找到温泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.43,0:07:57.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你还没死心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.55,0:08:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为又变冷了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.28,0:08:07.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 我果然还是觉得
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.54,0:08:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 还是去看一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.55,0:08:16.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你们上哪儿去
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.53,0:08:20.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是让人在意啊 稍微去看一下情况
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.30,0:08:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,温泉怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.46,0:08:26.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它说 要是找温泉的话
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.79,0:08:29.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还是去问一下刚才的那些人为好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.14,0:08:32.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对啊 还有这一招啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.58,0:08:36.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然只有脑袋的家伙就是聪明啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.95,0:08:54.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里是旧的矿场吧 大伙在哪里啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听着 好好听我说 敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.66,0:08:59.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,救命啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.41,0:09:04.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔卡 快救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.41,0:09:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.66,0:09:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴 不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.29,0:09:14.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.90,0:09:19.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要逃走的话都是这个下场 给我好好记牢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.93,0:09:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.05,0:09:22.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.56,0:09:29.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.35,0:09:31.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.53,0:09:32.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.89,0:09:37.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥 这是怎么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.94,0:09:39.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那些人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.11,0:09:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底发生了什么事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.68,0:09:46.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 温泉在什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.82,0:09:48.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偏偏在这种时候
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.35,0:09:51.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家不要过来
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.09,0:09:52.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.00,0:09:55.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁松大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:10:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 吵死了 出现逃跑者之后又有什么事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.55,0:10:03.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那些家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.75,0:10:06.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是那家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.19,0:10:10.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们在这里干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.21,0:10:12.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆 快逃吧 这些人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.77,0:10:14.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.20,0:10:16.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你闭嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.34,0:10:17.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.23,0:10:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被包围了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.07,0:10:38.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卡鲁松 为何如此喧闹
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.10,0:10:40.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看吧 伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 那个人是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.81,0:11:03.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.62,0:11:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.06,0:11:16.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是这些人的老大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:17.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.59,0:11:20.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,认识他吗 罗克希
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.53,0:11:47.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克 你还活着啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么 为什么会在这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:22.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,话说回来 你到这里来干什么 鬼剑士
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.73,0:12:26.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个 我们只是为了能够泡上温泉而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.99,0:12:28.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你骗谁
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.16,0:12:30.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.16,0:12:34.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬼剑士 就问你一个问题
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:37.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你那身手能不能为我们效力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:40.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你说什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.49,0:12:43.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想保住小命的话 这是最后的机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.33,0:12:51.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可没办法和你们这些 到处欺凌弱小的家伙好好相处啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.11,0:12:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还有 这个手臂和你们的可不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:02.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这么说 你是要与我们为敌了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.98,0:13:05.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是这么回事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.89,0:13:06.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,OK
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.95,0:13:11.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.30,0:13:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保护这里是我们的职责
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.48,0:13:17.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快放开
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.23,0:13:20.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家快住手
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.25,0:13:22.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.50,0:13:29.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不见了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.77,0:13:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.50,0:13:37.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.94,0:13:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉德大陆将会改变
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.96,0:13:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不变的东西就让它消失吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.26,0:14:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.75,0:14:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.03,0:14:14.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然把巴隆
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.20,0:14:19.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我站住
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.87,0:14:24.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,出于自身的考虑 还是不要抵抗的为好
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.00,0:14:28.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要不然的话就会和那个鬼剑士同样下场了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.59,0:14:30.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,带走
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:34.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 住手 快放开我
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.98,0:14:38.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.25,0:14:55.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然对巴隆做那样的事
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.03,0:15:00.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟要走到什么地方啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.87,0:15:01.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴 走你的路
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.04,0:15:11.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.99,0:15:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.76,0:15:19.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一二 哦呀
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:27.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怪不得觉得这么热 原来是这种地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.12,0:15:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,究竟在这种地方在干什么
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.98,0:15:31.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.32,0:15:43.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么东西
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.39,0:15:46.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你们闹出什么骚乱的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.11,0:15:49.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族的尸体就会增加的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:50.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.63,0:15:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就这些 已经没有什么了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.88,0:16:01.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你究竟把这些东西藏在什么地方
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.01,0:16:05.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么啊 那个机器人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.78,0:16:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 这个 玩具啊玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.70,0:16:12.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:17.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 这个不能拿走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.53,0:16:18.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放开
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.83,0:16:23.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧 好好干活的话就还给你
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.37,0:16:26.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,威力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.85,0:16:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.75,0:16:41.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.71,0:16:43.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敏泰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.44,0:16:45.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:49.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧 太好了 我很担心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.35,0:16:50.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其他的人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:54.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老人们和小孩虽然被抓住了但是没事
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.31,0:16:58.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把他们作为人质 任意驱使我们
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.89,0:17:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你说什么
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.31,0:17:01.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,巴尔雷娜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.27,0:17:03.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佟巴叔叔他
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.99,0:17:06.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然还是没能逃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.75,0:17:11.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奥尔卡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.65,0:17:37.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是族长吧 帮我们干点活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.05,0:17:44.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.56,0:17:50.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再靠近这座山了 快走
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.73,0:18:06.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克 费丽亚到了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.63,0:18:08.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.26,0:18:09.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经充分成长了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.71,0:18:11.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.49,0:18:21.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,热 这样一个劲地加热打算干什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.96,0:18:25.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,谁知道 他们怕冷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.67,0:18:42.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尽可能的把伤者带来了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.35,0:18:44.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,做得很好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.68,0:19:03.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人 请救救我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:07.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再忍耐一会 一定会成功的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.20,0:19:19.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班图族不是自豪感很强的一族吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.15,0:19:26.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥丢掉了班图族的自豪
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.59,0:19:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再也不相信哥哥了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你懂什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.70,0:19:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同伴被作为人质抓住了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.05,0:19:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了保护部族 我只有变成魔鬼丢掉灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.40,0:19:40.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别偷懒 让它烧得更旺些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.82,0:20:00.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,费丽亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.42,0:20:06.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟 难得的客人啊 请好好干活吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.48,0:20:37.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变热了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.64,0:20:38.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,终于快好了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.74,0:21:09.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.76,0:21:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.03,0:21:15.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像是红色的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.32,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纽梅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.77,0:21:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.22,0:21:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,伊鲁贝克大人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.59,0:21:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种力量的谜题解开的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.76,0:21:52.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,阿拉德大陆就会改变 一定会的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.04,0:21:57.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个神奇的花就是他们拼命的原因
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.93,0:22:01.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,活下来 巴隆
